
--- insert


first, find the target node			install/disks/pool  

only match parent+1

match "^\s{cp+1}

if column < target, listing=false
if column >= target, insert while listing=true



if no children, create a child

if children, add to end of children, if no child match, if child key exists, do nothing.



--- modify


first, find the target node

replace key:value-old:value-new

continue


--- remove


first, find the target node

continue to omit yaml as long as whitespace is > target
